This paper is about evolving artificial neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of machine learning. Specifically, the paper focuses on A-type artificial neural networks, which are a type of feedforward neural network. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
